{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1>Mijn eerste game met Pygame</h1>\n<p>Het tweede project wat ik voor mijn opleiding heb gemaakt was een game, gemaakt met Pygame. Pygame is een opensource game engine gemaakt in Python.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/35fa7/pygame1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 650px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 59.33774834437086%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"pygame euromast the game\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/a111b/pygame1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/aca85/pygame1.jpg 163w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/0954f/pygame1.jpg 325w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/a111b/pygame1.jpg 650w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/ce471/pygame1.jpg 975w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/bee4e/pygame1.jpg 1300w,\n/static/362918fd5b64a4fef64847e5d050e17a/35fa7/pygame1.jpg 1510w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Steven24K/Project-2-Game\">Bron code</a></p>\n<p>De game was origineel gebouwd voor Python 3.6, later heb ik een versie gemaakt die compatable is met Python 3.6. De dependency met de PostgreSQL database is komen te vervallen.</p>\n<h1>Euromast The Game</h1>\n<p>Doel spel: Zoveel mogelijk vragen over Rotterdam correct beantwoorden en als eerste de top van de Euromast bereiken. </p>\n<iframe width=\"900\" height=\"506\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/NOCupqNu5Ts\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe>","frontmatter":{"title":"Mijn eerste game met Pygame","date":"2017-01-28","category":"Projects"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/Mijn-eerste-game-in-pygame/"}}